item.title: Changelog
item.description: Changelog # All notable changes to this project are documented in this page. The format is based on Keep a Changelog. 1.6.4 - 2023-12-10 # Fixed # Error with generic avatar in 2022 #794 Assertion Error in some rare case #795 1.6.3 - 2023-12-09 # Added # Support for VRCSDK 3.5.x #787 Actually, previous version of AAO works well with VRCSDK 3.5.x / Unity 2022 with tiny bugs. I’ve fixed some bugs in Unity 2022 in this release.
